messages.title: Carol called on you
messages.content: Carol Woods and the Lib Dem team called to see you today.
Carol and the Lib Dems are fighting to get a fairer deal for the people of Durham.
Having been let down by Labour for so long, local people are ready for a change. Only Carol Woods can deliver that for Durham.
Carol is working hard to make a real difference for you and your family.

messages.title: The General Election is your chance to vote for a fresh start in Durham.

images.caption: Carol Woods talking to a constituent

leaflet.additionalNotes: The leaflet does not provide a specific election date or highlight detailed policies, nor does it mention the party leader of the Liberal Democrats or provide specific endorsements or quotes.
